text: Didymos may refer to: * 65803 Didymos, a near-Earth asteroid * Didymos (music theorist), ancient Greek music theorist * Several other ancient Greeks more commonly spelt Didymus, see Didymus (disambiguation) * Didymos I (1921–2014), Oriental Orthodox bishop == See also == * Didimus, a genus of beetles
title: Didymos
